Troubleshooting Tips
Issue: Permission Denied Errors
# Fix file permissions
chmod +x *.py
chmod -R u+rw ios-filesystem/
Issue: Module Import Errors
# Reinstall Python dependencies
pip3 install --user --upgrade pycryptodome

# Verify installation
python3 -c "import Crypto; print('Success')"
Issue: Empty Extraction Results
Verify keychain files exist: ls -la ios-filesystem/Library/Keychains/
Check file format matches expected structure
Ensure file reading logic handles encoding properly
Add debug print statements to trace execution
Issue: JSON Formatting Errors
# Validate JSON output
python3 -m json.tool keychain_report.json

# Pretty print for debugging
cat keychain_report.json | python3 -m json.tool > formatted.json
